This is a map I created last summer and never got to the point where I wanted to release it. i found the Folder with the map file in it and I fixed some bugs with it. I finished the layout with dev textures and I will texture this some other time. As for now I will leave it as is.

When I do get to texturing it will probably be a night version of this with great sounds and lighting.

Special Thanks goes out to DarkElfa for the idea for the name.
